# Baker Street Laboratory - API Test File
# Use this file with the REST Client extension in VSCodium
# Each request is separated by ###

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/v1

### 1. Test API Root Endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Get System Information
GET {{apiUrl}}/system/info
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Check System Health
GET {{apiUrl}}/system/health
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Conduct Research - Meaning of Life
POST {{apiUrl}}/research/conduct
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "query": "What is the meaning of life?",
    "output_dir": "research/api_output"
}

### 5. Conduct Research - Quantum Computing
POST {{apiUrl}}/research/conduct
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "query": "What are the latest developments in quantum computing?",
    "output_dir": "research/api_output"
}

### 6. Conduct Research - AI Ethics
POST {{apiUrl}}/research/conduct
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "query": "What are the ethical implications of artificial intelligence?",
    "output_dir": "research/api_output"
}

### 7. Get Research Status (replace session_id with actual ID from previous responses)
GET {{apiUrl}}/research/status/1a44a2d6
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. List All Reports
GET {{apiUrl}}/reports/list
Content-Type: application/json

### 9. Get Specific Report (replace report_id with actual ID)
GET {{apiUrl}}/reports/1a44a2d6
Content-Type: application/json

### 10. Test Error Handling - Invalid Endpoint
GET {{apiUrl}}/invalid/endpoint
Content-Type: application/json

### 11. Test Error Handling - Missing Query
POST {{apiUrl}}/research/conduct
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "output_dir": "research/api_output"
}

### 12. Test CORS - Options Request
OPTIONS {{apiUrl}}/research/conduct
Content-Type: application/json

